text: Sydney Parr is an American softball player. She attended North Little Rock High School in North Little Rock, Arkansas. She later attended the University of Arkansas, where she played outfield for the Arkansas Razorbacks softball team. ==References== ==External links== * *Arkansas bio Category:American softball players Category:Arkansas Razorbacks softball players Category:Living people Category:People from North Little Rock, Arkansas Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
